OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA band of
OL,6,Frain and strong winds in the far
OL,7,Fnorthwest will move slowly
OL,8,Fsoutheastwards overnight, with gales
OL,9,Fat times, reaching northern England by
OL,10,Fdawn. Largely dry ahead of it, with
OL,11,Fsome clear spells. A mild night for
OL,12,Fmost.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FRain and strong winds
OL,15,Fcontinuing to move southeastwards
OL,16,Fduring Thursday. Still some sunshine
OL,17,Fahead of this, with bright spells and
OL,18,Fshowers following. Feeling colder
OL,19,Flater in the north.
